text:
> Sports Is the SEC down? League depth a question at midway point FILE - In this Oct. 17, 2015, file photo, LSU players huddle before an NCAA college football game against Florida in Baton Rouge, La. The Tigers haven't played the most imposing schedule but are coming off a 35-28 win over Florida and are the only remaining unbeaten team in the SEC. (AP Photo/Gerald Herbert, File)
